Greetings --

I had a consistent leak on my 3-4 valve cover for a while.  Turns out that the tiniest little gouge was causing it.  I used a sanding wheel on the dremel, smoothed it out, and voila, no more leak.  And I'm talking small gouge too, maybe 1/64"?  

Charles
